JOHANNESBURG - South Africa's athletics star Wayde van Niekerk is in it for the long run, tying the knot to Chesney Campbell at the weekend.  The 400m Gold Olympian made the announcement on all his social media accounts on Sunday morning.  Van Niekerk posted a black-and-white photograph of him and his new bride, describing her as the girl of his dreams.  The athlete previously provided details of their relationship on social media, posting photos of them together.    In December 2016, van Niekerk also posted his joy when Chesney said "yes."  eNCA